5596 5952 Taken together , these two decisions , plus one yet to come in a case involving Harold M. Ickes , former deputy White House chief of staff , amounted to what campaign finance lawyers said was probably the last chance for Ms. Reno to allow an outside prosecutor to examine the actions of senior White House officials in financing Mr. Clinton 's re-election .
